me two minutes?

576
00:53:26,680 --> 00:53:28,193
How's the pregnancy going?

577
00:53:28,400 --> 00:53:30,356
Oh. Lumping along.

578
00:53:30,560 --> 00:53:32,118
Still at the flat?
That's right.

579
00:53:32,320 --> 00:53:34,072
The three of you?
Four soon.

580
00:53:34,280 --> 00:53:37,078
