608
00:54:54,840 --> 00:54:56,876
Doris, what a thing to say.

609
00:54:57,080 --> 00:55:00,117
Well, what am I expected
to say, then?

610
00:55:00,920 --> 00:55:02,717
Wait a minute.

611
00:55:04,360 --> 00:55:05,759
Leave it to me, sir.

612
00:55:05,960 --> 00:55:08,235
[***]

613
00:55:15,880 --> 00:55:19,190
