Shut up!

647
00:58:48,400 --> 00:58:50,675
I'll tell you what this
little episode's taught me.

648
00:58:51,040 --> 00:58:53,873
It's taught me what it feels like
to look like the back end of a bus

649
00:58:54,080 --> 00:58:56,514
and sit around every night
with nothing to do.

650
00:58:58,200 --> 00:58:59,428
You bitch.

651
00:59:02,040 --> 00:59:03,393
We're not crying, are we?

652
00:59:03,920 --> 00:59:06,480
Oh, here we go again.
Just like my mother.

653
00:59:06,720 --> 00:59:09,917
She always used to cry
when the announcer
on the radio said goodnight.

654
00:59:10,160 --> 00:59:12,515
Lucky for you you're pregnant,
otherwise I might smack your face.

655
00:59:12,720 --> 00:59:14,711
You think you're one
of the world's beauties.

656
00:59:14,920 --> 00:59:16,558
At least I'm not one of its freaks.

657
00:59:17,360 --> 00:59:19,715
I think I'll smack it anyway!
GEORGY: No, she's right.

658
00:59:19,920 --> 00:59:22,195
I'm like the back of a bus,
and my face is too fat.

659
00:59:22,400 --> 00:59:24,994
